additional_info:
By tjxwork 2019-09-13
v0.5
更新内容：适合配新的首页界面、新版首页不再屏蔽侧边栏（暂时不知道怎么屏蔽……）
（最近B站搞了新版的首页，和旧的首页对比改了几个id名称，侧边栏就直接没分开给标记，暂时不知道要怎么才能选择。旧版依然是可以屏蔽侧边栏的。）
如果想屏蔽其他区块，请复制下表对应项目粘到样式表（全加上就只剩下“顶部导航条”了(新版的侧边栏也会在)）

<code>
    /*分区块中的横条广告(全站)*/
    .banner-card {display: none;}
    /*分区块中的横条广告(全站) 旧版*/
    .gg-floor-module {display: none;}


    /*最顶行(幻灯片行)*/
    #reportFirst1 {display: none;}
    /*最顶行(幻灯片行)旧版*/
    #chief_recommend {display: none;}


    /*推广(顶部第二行)*/
    #reportFirst2 {display: none;}
    /*推广(顶部第二行) 旧版*/
    #home_popularize {display: none;}


    /*直播(顶部第三行)*/
    #bili_live {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="0"] {display: none;}


    /*动画*/
    #bili_douga {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="1"] {display: none;}


    /*番剧*/
    #bili_anime {display: none;}
    /*番剧 旧版*/
    #bili_bangumi {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="2"] {display: none;}


    /*国创*/
    #bili_guochuang {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="3"] {display: none;}


    /*漫画 旧版*/
    #bili_manga {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="4"] {display: none;}


    /*音乐*/
    #bili_music {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="5"] {display: none;}


    /*舞蹈*/
    #bili_dance {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="6"] {display: none;}


    /*游戏*/
    #bili_game {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="7"] {display: none;}


    /*科技*/
    #bili_technology {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="8"] {display: none;}


    /*数码*/
    #bili_digital {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="9"] {display: none;}


    /*生活*/
    #bili_life {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="10"] {display: none;}


    /*鬼畜*/
    #bili_kichiku {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="11"] {display: none;}


    /*广告*/
    #bili_ad {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="13"] {display: none;}


    /*时尚*/
    #bili_fashion {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="12"] {display: none;}


    /*娱乐*/
    #bili_ent {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="14"] {display: none;}


    /*专栏*/
    #bili_read {display: none;}
    /*专栏 旧版*/
    #bili_article {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="15"] {display: none;}


    /*电影*/
    #bili_movie {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="16"] {display: none;}


    /*TV剧*/
    #bili_teleplay {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="17"] {display: none;}


    /*影视*/
    #bili_cinephile {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="18"] {display: none;}


    /*纪录片*/
    #bili_documentary {display: none;}
    .nav-list>[sortindex="19"] {display: none;}


    /*特别推荐(最后一行)*/
    #bili_report_spe_rec {display: none;}
    /*特别推荐(最后一行) 旧版*/
    #special_recommend {display: none;}

</code>



